DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       "v.circle" will create "polygon" circle(s) around points read  from  an
       existing "site_lists" file.  The "site_lists" point(s) will be the cen-
       ter(s) for those circle(s) with one  circle  created  per  point.   The
       "polygon"  circle(s)  will  be  written  to a binary vector file.  Each
       "polygon" circle will have 361 points with each point on the circumfer-
       ence of the circle representing 1 degree of arc.



